  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3000 Bakeries Closing Position",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jayawardena, President of the All Ceylon Bakery Owners' Association, said that bakery owners are facing more difficulties due to the 300 percent increase in the price of bakery ingredients and the price of a 50 kg wheat flour package has increased by 1000 rupees.",
        "He said that if this situation continues, the yield of bakery food will increase and it will greatly affect the general public, adding that about 3000 bakeries have been closed due to the current economic crisis."
      ],
